# Documentation Workflows

On each feature/change:
- Update [memory-bank/activeContext.md](mdc:memory-bank/activeContext.md): current focus, recent changes, next steps.
- Update [memory-bank/systemPatterns.md](mdc:memory-bank/systemPatterns.md): navigation routes, feature modules, state flows.
- Update [memory-bank/techContext.md](mdc:memory-bank/techContext.md): configs, dependencies, schema.
- Update [memory-bank/progress.md](mdc:memory-bank/progress.md): done, pending, known issues.

Testing & Verification:
- Run Flutter tests: `flutter test` for unit/widget tests in `test/`.
- Run integration tests if present: `flutter test integration_test`.
- Use `flutter analyze` to enforce lints; keep analyzer clean.

Commit Style:
- Small, incremental edits with clear messages describing intent and impact.
- Reference updated Memory Bank files in commit body when applicable.